data.description: **PRICE IMPROVEMENT!!** This charming brick home offers a cozy retreat on a spacious 1.48-acre lot, providing a perfect blend of comfort and outdoor opportunities. With main floor living, the convenience is unmatched. The presence of two wood-burning fireplaces adds warmth and character, creating inviting spaces for relaxation. The expansive yard opens up a world of possibilities, whether it's for outdoor activities or keeping animals. A perfect haven for those who appreciate both comfort and the joys of nature.   Square footage figures are provided as a courtesy estimate only and were obtained from previous MLS listing.  Buyer is advised to obtain an independent measurement.
